    "title": "UK Contractor Survival Index",
    "description": "How long UK contractor-sector businesses survive, by 1, 2, 3, 4 and 5 years after formation, built from ONS Business Demography birth-cohort data for SIC groups 62 (computer programming and IT consultancy), 70 (head offices and management consultancy) and 71 (architecture and engineering), against the all-industries UK average.",
